**********************
| For module NODE_DB |
**********************

-> Create a node from DB External.

-> You create nodes from "admin/settings/crear_nodos". You find a button that construct the nodes.

-> Use hook_cron for update the nodes from db external.

********************************
| For module NODE_DB_EXTENSION |
********************************

-> Is a extension that add a new rows of db external to new nodes for your drupal site.

-> Only use cron for do this. Don't have a path where you administer.

NOTES:

-> The file baseDeDatos.php is a DAO for connect to DB external.

-> The directory LOG is use for register some errors.
